{"id": "ChIJYYyO5Ye4woAR0qhSVgRmlvE", "rating": 4.1, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_EXPENSIVE", "userRatingCount": 1608, "displayName": {"text": "Chosun Galbee", "languageCode": "en"}, "editorialSummary": {"text": "Korean BBQ spot featuring a menu of grilled meats, hot pot & noodles served in a modern space.", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJYYyO5Ye4woAR0qhSVgRmlvE/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21OVVdqSkdZWFIzWjBwSVVIUlZhRTlwWHpoQlgyYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "An OG of K-Town you can’t go wrong here. Classic menu, classic flavors, all done really well. Their side dishes are straight out of Korea. Their meats are high quality. Their neng myun is one of the best in the city. It’s great for large groups, families and date night. Highly recommend.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "An OG of K-Town you can’t go wrong here. Classic menu, classic flavors, all done really well. Their side dishes are straight out of Korea. Their meats are high quality. Their neng myun is one of the best in the city. It’s great for large groups, families and date night. Highly recommend.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "D L", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/105200650454223628344/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV_g3euTcUav-H6qYE7E0qzf6ksFk93S6ZoUFb1Awkz8IRsmrJnKQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-18T03:24:09.342802713Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21OVVdqSkdZWFIzWjBwSVVIUlZhRTlwWHpoQlgyYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21OVVdqSkdZWFIzWjBwSVVIUlZhRTlwWHpoQlgyYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2b887e58e8c61:0xf19666045652a8d2"}, {"name": "places/ChIJYYyO5Ye4woAR0qhSVgRmlvE/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tJNFJrOXFSVVpPV201VWRIbFhaVFZFYm5WR2JGRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "Excellent side dishes and generous portions of meat combos.\nThe pan fried fish appetizer dish was the best I’ve had in a long long while.\nSome of the meats are so so.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Excellent side dishes and generous portions of meat combos.\nThe pan fried fish appetizer dish was the best I’ve had in a long long while.\nSome of the meats are so so.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Jong Lee", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/117076314802225950248/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWsj66d8DdmBbxiBfPXwcsaGu37_5Q5dlKhqvY11hATgPvGuCHOqw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba7"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-07T04:08:31.212373047Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tJNFJrOXFSVVpPV201VWRIbFhaVFZFYm5WR2JGRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tJNFJrOXFSVVpPV201VWRIbFhaVFZFYm5WR2JGRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2b887e58e8c61:0xf19666045652a8d2"}, {"name": "places/ChIJYYyO5Ye4woAR0qhSVgRmlvE/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xNM05tUnNTWFE0YW1zNFdsTmlSR3B3YldGdFpuYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "8 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Five Stars\n\nChosun Galbee is my hands-down favorite Korean barbecue in Los Angeles. The moment you walk in, the atmosphere sets the tone—warm, energetic, and refined without being stuffy. There’s an open-air patio shaded by ficus trees, an elegant dining room with modern wood and stone touches, and the unmistakable sizzle and aroma of top-quality meats grilling at every table.\n\nTheir signature galbee is the best I’ve ever had—beautifully marbled short ribs marinated in a savory-sweet soy blend that caramelizes perfectly over the flame. The bulgogi is tender and flavorful, while the prime rib and ribeye cuts rival any steakhouse in the city. The seafood is equally impressive—the sea bass and shrimp are fresh, delicately seasoned, and grilled to perfection.\n\nBanchan are abundant and thoughtfully prepared, from the crisp kimchi to the delicate bean sprouts and seasoned spinach. The japchae, with glass noodles and vegetables, is silky and aromatic, and their bibimbap is a colorful masterpiece that balances texture and heat. On warmer nights, the cold buckwheat noodles (naengmyeon) are a refreshing standout.\n\nTheir full bar deserves mention—soju flights, Korean beers, and a surprisingly strong whiskey and cocktail list make it easy to pair drinks with any dish. Service is attentive without hovering, and the staff knows the menu inside out. Whether for a date, a client dinner, or a night out with friends, Chosun Galbee nails it every time.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Five Stars\n\nChosun Galbee is my hands-down favorite Korean barbecue in Los Angeles. The moment you walk in, the atmosphere sets the tone—warm, energetic, and refined without being stuffy. There’s an open-air patio shaded by ficus trees, an elegant dining room with modern wood and stone touches, and the unmistakable sizzle and aroma of top-quality meats grilling at every table.\n\nTheir signature galbee is the best I’ve ever had—beautifully marbled short ribs marinated in a savory-sweet soy blend that caramelizes perfectly over the flame. The bulgogi is tender and flavorful, while the prime rib and ribeye cuts rival any steakhouse in the city. The seafood is equally impressive—the sea bass and shrimp are fresh, delicately seasoned, and grilled to perfection.\n\nBanchan are abundant and thoughtfully prepared, from the crisp kimchi to the delicate bean sprouts and seasoned spinach. The japchae, with glass noodles and vegetables, is silky and aromatic, and their bibimbap is a colorful masterpiece that balances texture and heat. On warmer nights, the cold buckwheat noodles (naengmyeon) are a refreshing standout.\n\nTheir full bar deserves mention—soju flights, Korean beers, and a surprisingly strong whiskey and cocktail list make it easy to pair drinks with any dish. Service is attentive without hovering, and the staff knows the menu inside out. Whether for a date, a client dinner, or a night out with friends, Chosun Galbee nails it every time.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Paul Mark Morris", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/115290292625277527782/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXyIoEKQ41_vyg-vMs16jWg48oclAupnXKSrVYUCgAI_3vnt_Uk=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2025-11-10T13:07:13.981045626Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xNM05tUnNTWFE0YW1zNFdsTmlSR3B3YldGdFpuYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xNM05tUnNTWFE0YW1zNFdsTmlSR3B3YldGdFpuYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2b887e58e8c61:0xf19666045652a8d2"}, {"name": "places/ChIJYYyO5Ye4woAR0qhSVgRmlvE/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURXeWNQcE13EAE", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "6 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "There is valet parking. (Valet fee is $4)\nI ordered Neangmyun, and it is amazingly delicious. However, I didn't understand putting vinegar and mustard in disposable bins. You just need big bins that is more convenient and also good at environment. Prime Galbi was good, but the onion was ignored how to eat. Overall, the interior was fancy and service was good. Many korean people recommended this place. I love it.\n\n9/11/2025\nEverything is so nice right now.\nNo more disposal bins.\nWe had a lunch menu and it was good!\n\n12/2025\n\nGalbi was sweet to me.\nService is amazing.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "There is valet parking. (Valet fee is $4)\nI ordered Neangmyun, and it is amazingly delicious. However, I didn't understand putting vinegar and mustard in disposable bins. You just need big bins that is more convenient and also good at environment. Prime Galbi was good, but the onion was ignored how to eat. Overall, the interior was fancy and service was good. Many korean people recommended this place. I love it.\n\n9/11/2025\nEverything is so nice right now.\nNo more disposal bins.\nWe had a lunch menu and it was good!\n\n12/2025\n\nGalbi was sweet to me.\nService is amazing.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "J Shin", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/116143389960133051013/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKDG8eRv05PiY_9eW2X5dCMC_W4SXhF-OHFjLZv6XWJCMHOUu4=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-02T05:25:23.694588790Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURXeWNQcE13EAE&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURXeWNQcE13EAE!2m1!1s0x80c2b887e58e8c61:0xf19666045652a8d2"}, {"name": "places/ChIJYYyO5Ye4woAR0qhSVgRmlvE/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tkSFQyb3hlVkptTWxWUldsOXZPVU51ZEhWWmQzYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "11 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Our cute Korean friend took us to this fabulous Korean BBQ in Korea Town. We loved it! The Jap chae was fabulous. It was a great way to all share a meal. We had a private room and the service was wonderful.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Our cute Korean friend took us to this fabulous Korean BBQ in Korea Town. We loved it! The Jap chae was fabulous. It was a great way to all share a meal. We had a private room and the service was wonderful.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Janet Marroquin", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/115919853479642623217/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX8i7mdoFH5hu2WjYOX0aP7UJqB4FMq4hDODQ23xyoLPOyeKpFi=s1